title: Stacey Abrams’ finance report: strong earnings, with debt no longer a problem -  The Atlanta Journal Constitution
content: Stacey Abrams’ finance report: strong earnings, with debt no longer a problem   The Atlanta Journal Constitution
description: Four years ago, Stacey Abrams’ struggles with debt became a favorite Republican attack during her run for governor. As she wages a second bid for Georgia’s top job, financial disclosures show that won’t be an issue this time.
